# Next.js 16 & React

- Use Next.js 16 App Router conventions; components under `src/app/` are RSC by default.
- Mark client components with `"use client"` only when needed (hooks, browser APIs, event handlers).
- Prefer server components for data fetching; use `async` server components or server actions where appropriate.
- Use path aliases: `@/`, `@components/`, `@lib/`, `@app/`, `@features/`, `@server/`, `@types/`.
- Lint and format with Biome only (`pnpm check`, `pnpm check --write`). No ESLint or Prettier.
- Colocate components and styles; use shadcn/ui (new-york) and CVA for variants.
